WEBVTT

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:14.519
Sigh, these days...

00:01:14.879 --> 00:01:16.599
charging a phone is really inconvenient.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.519
Why aren't you answering the phone?

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:27.519
What are you doing?

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:50.319
Just as I thought.

00:01:50.959 --> 00:01:51.959
There's something going on between them.

00:02:04.879 --> 00:02:06.079
Driver, follow them.

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:09.400
Chen Fan.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.479
Do you know how dangerous that was just now?

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:12.960
If I had arrived a step later, you would have...

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.840
Why were you following Zhou Honghai?

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:18.120
I don't know why either.

00:02:19.479 --> 00:02:21.199
Brother Honghai and Manager Liu of Longshi Group

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:22.159
would join forces.

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:23.919
I must investigate this matter thoroughly.

00:02:23.919 --> 00:02:24.840
What Longshi?

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:26.520
You don't know how deep the waters run at Longshi,

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.759
or how complex their background is.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.479
No, I don't understand.

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:31.360
How do you know about these things regarding Longshi?

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:31.960
I...

00:02:35.479 --> 00:02:37.039
Because I've died once.

00:02:38.919 --> 00:02:40.919
In my previous life, before I was killed by a car,

00:02:41.039 --> 00:02:42.759
I was investigating their case.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:48.840
Previous life? Hit by a car?

00:02:49.879 --> 00:02:51.759
I know this sounds like crazy talk,

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:54.840
but please believe me.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.120
No, stop talking.

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:03.080
You said you were hit by a car in your previous life?

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:08.759
Before I was killed by a car in my previous life,

00:03:09.439 --> 00:03:11.199
I heard them saying

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:13.120
they wouldn't let anyone around me go,

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:14.840
starting with you.

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:18.080
So I broke up with you because I was afraid you'd get hurt.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.319
On the day of the proposal,

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:23.280
I had a terrible headache that night.

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:26.080
Two lives flashed through my mind at once.

00:03:27.639 --> 00:03:29.319
One is this time,

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:31.680
we took the college entrance exam together,

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:34.319
got into Yunhai University together,

00:03:34.479 --> 00:03:35.759
and lived in Yunhai together.

00:03:37.639 --> 00:03:39.400
The other one is our previous life.

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:40.879
I was killed by a car.

00:03:43.479 --> 00:03:45.280
I didn't know which one was real.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:54.120
They are all real.

00:04:04.039 --> 00:04:05.560
After you left in the previous life,

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.919
I lived in regret every day.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:12.120
Just like that, twenty years passed.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.360
Until I closed my eyes on the hospital bed and opened them again,

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:19.439
and I was back before the college entrance exam.

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:22.480
You left too early in the previous life.

00:04:23.920 --> 00:04:25.279
So this time I wanted to hurry,

00:04:25.279 --> 00:04:26.800
I wanted to be with you sooner.

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:28.720
I was afraid this was a dream.

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:29.680
I was afraid of repeating the same mistakes.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.000
I was afraid there wasn't enough time.

00:04:36.399 --> 00:04:37.040
You also...

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:40.759
I've also died once.

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:00.959
Chen Fan.

00:05:08.759 --> 00:05:10.439
I'm sorry, I shouldn't have broken up with you.

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:15.120
No matter what happens in this life,

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:17.759
we will face it together.

00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:22.120
I won't let you get hurt again.

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:35.560
Zhou Honghai

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:37.240
That's not what you said back then.

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:39.519
You just said to add some kind of

00:05:39.519 --> 00:05:41.279
Easter egg to liven things up for everyone.

00:05:41.639 --> 00:05:42.360
But now,

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.160
not only is the game banned online,

00:05:44.439 --> 00:05:46.000
but Fan-ge and Brother Liang have been arrested.

00:05:46.279 --> 00:05:47.240
Why did this happen?

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:49.680
Wen Jie, you say this has nothing to do with me?

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:52.480
Back then, wasn't it when you were operating

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.160
that you didn't hide it well and got caught by Cyber Police?

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.519
How does it have nothing to do with you?

00:05:56.079 --> 00:05:58.040
If you hadn't dragged me out drinking back then,

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:59.879
and while I was dizzy from drinking,

00:06:00.079 --> 00:06:02.240
made me add some game code...

00:06:02.519 --> 00:06:03.920
Now that something has happened,

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:05.560
you want to wash your hands of it, right?

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:06.079
Hey.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:07.240
It's not washing my hands.

00:06:09.040 --> 00:06:11.560
I was clean to begin with.

00:06:11.759 --> 00:06:12.120
Look.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:14.920
"Add some spice to Brother Liang and Fan-ge's game."

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:20.399
"Can't let them look down on me."

00:06:22.439 --> 00:06:23.360
See that clearly?

00:06:24.759 --> 00:06:26.279
It's recorded very clearly.

00:06:26.759 --> 00:06:28.639
You were the only one who acted back then.

00:06:30.279 --> 00:06:31.759
You planned this all along, didn't you?

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:35.240
How can this be a scheme?

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:37.680
I was just afraid you'd forget since you drank too much,

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:38.920
so I recorded it for you.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.680
Despicable.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.759
Enough.

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:44.519
We're in the same boat now.

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:46.720
Continue to do as I say.

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:48.519
Tell me Chen Fan's every move.

00:06:48.519 --> 00:06:49.160
And Liang Shichu.

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:50.040
In your dreams!

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:53.439
You want me to help you harm Brother Liang and Fan-ge?

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:54.839
Impossible.

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:57.160
Worst case, I'll just go surrender.

00:06:57.759 --> 00:06:58.680
How you instigated me,

00:06:58.680 --> 00:06:59.920
and how you filmed the video to threaten me—

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:00.839
I'll tell them everything.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:02.480
And drag you to prison with me.

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:04.879
Alright, Wen Jie.

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:06.879
Then think it over clearly.

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:08.759
If you really want to do that,

00:07:09.879 --> 00:07:10.680
I'm waiting for you.

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.199
Zhou Honghai, you...

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:18.279
Just you wait.

00:07:18.839 --> 00:07:21.279
In 2000, the entrance exam and a successful confession.

00:07:21.279 --> 00:07:23.360
Until the summer of 2000 when DomainNet was built.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.360
Then in 2001, Guo Shuai had his accident.

00:07:27.879 --> 00:07:29.839
Finally, your car accident.

00:07:30.759 --> 00:07:31.959
You said before,

00:07:31.959 --> 00:07:33.079
before the car accident,

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:34.360
you were interning at a law firm,

00:07:34.439 --> 00:07:35.959
and were working on the Longshi case.

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:36.560
That's right.

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:39.319
It was a major transnational smuggling case.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:42.040
Under the guise of import-export trade,

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:43.480
they were trafficking human organs.

00:07:43.759 --> 00:07:45.040
At the time, I happened to be in charge of

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:46.279
organizing some evidentiary materials.

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:50.240
I had crucial evidence that could bring them down.

00:07:50.959 --> 00:07:53.240
Smuggling human organs.

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:55.399
Longshi really has some nerve.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:58.839
But according to my memories of my previous life,

00:07:58.839 --> 00:07:59.879
Longshi Group, afterwards,

00:07:59.879 --> 00:08:02.279
never had a scandal like smuggling exposed.

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.720
Could it be because...

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:09.959
Your death?

00:08:11.439 --> 00:08:12.079
Yes.

00:08:12.759 --> 00:08:13.639
Because of my death,

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.079
the evidence was snatched away at that time.

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:18.560
Without the evidence,

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:21.600
the matter naturally fizzled out.

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:23.759
They continued their crimes brazenly,

00:08:23.759 --> 00:08:24.720
and grew stronger.

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:28.639
It's not your fault.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:30.480
Blame Longshi for being too ruthless.

00:08:30.959 --> 00:08:32.399
You tried your hardest to protect the evidence.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:36.360
So after I came back,

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:39.080
the first thing I did was investigate Longshi Group.

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:41.159
But so far, I've only found

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.360
that they are doing some real estate development,

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:44.200
micro-lending,

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:46.519
and businesses like digital hardware trading.

00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:51.399
Then before,

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:53.799
the person who threatened and attacked you,

00:08:53.799 --> 00:08:55.039
do you remember who it was?

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.679
Every time I think about it,

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:00.720
my head hurts like it's going to split open.

00:09:01.759 --> 00:09:03.200
It's okay, don't force it.

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:06.639
Then do you know a person named Zhao Xiaozhuo?

00:09:07.159 --> 00:09:08.679
He is the driver who hit you before.

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:11.879
I... I don't know him.

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:16.919
Then it seems now,

00:09:17.159 --> 00:09:18.759
the whole timeline is stretched too long.

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:20.879
There are too many uncertain factors in between.

00:09:20.879 --> 00:09:21.559
Right.

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:23.519
And we don't even have a reason to call the police.

00:09:24.519 --> 00:09:25.759
The police can't just,

00:09:25.919 --> 00:09:27.559
based on what might happen in the future,

00:09:27.559 --> 00:09:28.559
go and arrest people.

00:09:30.559 --> 00:09:32.519
Since we can't prevent it in advance,

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:35.440
then we'll keep a close eye on Longshi's movements.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.159
Wait for them to show their hand,

00:09:37.159 --> 00:09:38.320
and we'll deal with it then.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.240
Mm.

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:46.799
Hello? Who is it?

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:48.039
Chen Fan.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.120
I'm out.

00:09:49.519 --> 00:09:50.159
Brother Liang.

00:09:50.399 --> 00:09:51.080
You're out?

00:09:51.639 --> 00:09:52.320
That's great.

00:09:52.799 --> 00:09:54.000
No, it's not good.

00:09:54.159 --> 00:09:55.039
It's Wen Jie.

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:56.080
He said that regarding the game,

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:57.600
he was the one who planted the prohibited content.

00:09:58.120 --> 00:09:59.159
He came to surrender.

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:00.159
What?

00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:02.559
Why are you doing this to yourself?

00:10:03.279 --> 00:10:04.320
I told you long ago,

00:10:04.679 --> 00:10:05.639
with that video recording,

00:10:06.159 --> 00:10:07.759
no one will believe what you say.

00:10:08.519 --> 00:10:09.840
I think you shouldn't waste your energy.

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:11.159
I will also take good care of your family.

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:12.279
Or else what?

00:10:17.799 --> 00:10:19.799
I will also take good care of your sister.

00:10:20.759 --> 00:10:21.759
If you dare touch my sister,

00:10:22.639 --> 00:10:23.639
I will tell Chen Fan,

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:24.639
tell the police.

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:25.639
Wen Jie.

00:10:26.519 --> 00:10:28.679
Do you think they will believe what you say,

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:31.440
or that crystal clear video recording?

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:36.639
Think about it carefully.

00:10:37.840 --> 00:10:39.679
Will you take the blame for all this yourself,

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:42.240
and ensure your sister's safety?

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:43.720
Or do you insist on being stubborn,

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:45.399
and in the end, not only fail to bring me down,

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.360
but also ruin your sister?

00:10:50.759 --> 00:10:51.440
Think again.